Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:17.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\fs50\an7\frz270\bord1.7\3c&H1A1818&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1200,109)}——状况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\fs50\an7\frz270\bord1.7\3c&H1A1818&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(140,403)}依旧胶着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一之濑已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但状况依然胶着不变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,正中A班下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\fs40\an7\frz270\bord1.7\3c&H1A1818&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1183,140)}继续
